        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="text-neon-blue">Targeting/Advertising Cookies:</strong> These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners.
          They may be used to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant advertisements on other sites.
        </li>
      </ul>

